dc_title_s: West Indies, Virgin Islands, approaches to Road Harbour (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by contours, spot heights, and hachures. "From various sources to 1985." "Copyright 1995 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Inset: Tortola (U.K.), Road Harbour. Scale 1:15,000. Includes compilation diagram and tidal information. Map no.25611 This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
